</li>
<li><strong><a class="auto" href="/a/%E8%A5%BF%E6%B2%99%E8%AB%B8%E5%B3%B6">西沙諸島</a></strong>※</li>
<li><strong><a class="auto" href="/a/%E5%8D%97%E6%B2%99%E8%AB%B8%E5%B3%B6">南沙諸島</a></strong>※</li>
<li>釣<a class="auto-hdn" href="/a/%E9%AD%9A">魚</a><a class="auto-hdn" href="/a/%E5%B3%B6">島</a>（<strong><a class="auto" href="/a/%E5%B0%96%E9%96%A3%E8%AB%B8%E5%B3%B6">尖閣諸島</a></strong>）※</li>
<li><strong><a class="auto" href="/a/%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE">台湾</a></strong>※</li>
<li><strong><a class="auto" href="/a/%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6">南丫島</a></strong>
</li>
</ul>
